# ACCEPTANCE_EVIDENCE_PLAN.md

## Purpose

Plan design-stage acceptance evidence for {{ project.name }}.

This optional template maps design-stage requirements to evidence categories. It is not a runtime trace, test implementation, eval harness, or proof of live system behavior.

## Scope

- Design-stage requirement categories.
- Evidence categories.
- Evidence source row references.
- Review status.
- Gaps and follow-up items.

## Source Use

Reference source rows by identifier only. Use only rows approved for design summary unless owner-review rows have been accepted, revised, or deferred.

| source row | decision | evidence handling |
|---|---|---|
| SRC-### | usable for design summary | Evidence category reference only |
| SRC-### | owner review required | Not used unless resolved |
| SRC-### | excluded from repo | Not used |

