## Prohibited Content

- Runtime test code or eval harness implementation.
- Raw source bulk copy.
- Sensitive requirement text.
- Real operational evidence content.
- C# source, solution, project, XAML, build assets, scripts, or binaries.
- PLC/device code.
- Live target write support or external mutation.
- GitHub Actions or cloud CI.
- IP, port, tag value, live parameter, secret, private input, live config, credential, account, or equipment detail.

## Approval Boundary

This document plans evidence only. Running tests, generating evidence artifacts, implementing graders, integrating gates, or validating live systems requires separate approval.

## Review Checklist

- Evidence entries are design-stage categories only.
- Source-use decisions are followed.
- Owner-review sources are not used before resolution.
- Excluded sources remain outside target content.
- No runtime or live evidence is generated.
- Prohibited content is absent.
